text: Dzhamba () is a rural locality (a selo) in Vostochny Selsoviet, Ikryaninsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 39 km from Astrakhan, 6 km from Ikryanoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ikryaninsky District
title: Dzhamba
